Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了  給您草莓口味的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫夫路這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.83,0:00:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「大家  非常感謝你們今天能來」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「跟我們一起玩吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「那麼  開始囉」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.76,0:00:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去客流量不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  能不能擺脫現狀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為此我們才在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是莫夫路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們湊近點看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.45,0:01:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鯊魚?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是演出內容嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\bord1\blur3\3a&H80\pos(1050,715)}{\fad(500,1000)}泳池很危險!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬  不是告訴你不要出去的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常慚愧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我是大海的種族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要迎接各位來賓的話  果然還是要在泳池裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你被水淋濕以後  超嚇人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會把人直接嚇死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你頭一回看見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之你去機械室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遺憾萬分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然認為自己的特長是在水裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什  什…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是楓葉大陸和這裡連接的大門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘輝建設伊始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了從那邊運送材料過來而建成的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那  那也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:05:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家的故鄉  魔…魔法王國嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經沒在用了  所以應該嚴密封鎖了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼會滲水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  總之我先把設備部的人叫來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩位在這裡看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這地方不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始這裡就是我的城池
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們全都老老實實聽我們的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不聽話的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女海盜五十鈴魯哈不會輕饒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還  還算在接受範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你們去把礙事的都收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情不能容忍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心我吃了你們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禁斷的兄弟之愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的粉絲?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我是你的粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很關注你的爆料…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,野馬分鬃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像已經開始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  身體前傾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:07:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你陪我一起藏起來  真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事  身體前傾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超讚  身體前傾中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊修理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了  莫夫路它們遇到危機了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家  請大聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒來魔法之丘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它是鐵鬍子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在楓葉大陸的海上胡亂非為的海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難不成是從地下的門那裡來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大門這邊不是寶藏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過把這些女人小孩抓去賣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是能賣不少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本大人是海盜鐵鬍子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要抓你們  老實點待著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼要開演了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「才不會讓你們得逞」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是同道中人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣    要不要一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「才不會跟你們同流合污」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓到的女人可是隨你們處置的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗是徒勞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堤拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叛變了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實點聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小的們  上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「去死吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「Mother  Puffer」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左右摟膝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉媞琺大人  趕緊回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很危險…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可兒江大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼輕易的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  公主被抓住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小的們  開宴會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  這邊要兩瓶酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  馬上拿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.94,0:10:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刨冰  草莓和檸檬各一份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  話說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,映子小姐為什麼知道海狗說的是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:11:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到能活捉楓葉大陸的公主大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  酒還沒上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轉身搬攔捶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊接過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常用心的節目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之先裝的老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙  為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中條
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬這傢伙終於開始吃人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬喬喬喬…喬先生是為了救救救…救椎菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬先生…好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代理經理  您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.58,0:12:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  是時候來那個了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就等這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那三人處刑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新來的  你來動手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:13:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳板  跳板  跳板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.28,0:13:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堤拉米  你認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬卡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  我不會做把同伴推下去這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堤拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會救你的  照我說的去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬卡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳板  跳板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想騙過敵人先要騙過自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你騙不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那先站到板子的邊緣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那先站到板子的邊緣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼千斗妹妹  你是最後一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有些對不起  還請…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼反過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開炮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在開炮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可兒江同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過來  跟我一起逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉媞琺大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經理小姐  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反擊開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同伴來救我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家要為他們加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站哪邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饒不了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然很強
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人集中在舞台中央偏左  不要射擊那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3號  動作太慢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一發快點裝填
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  發射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鯊魚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海盜們投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可賀  可喜可賀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草莓糖漿黏糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢這樣對我  別以為就這麼完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個  我們這裡可是損失慘重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要負責賠償  必須賠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管呢  隨便你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說了必須賠就必須賠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真嚇人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶  媽媽  下次再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在這個夏天裡  你要在這裡做白工
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我盡全力為來賓服務
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰要做啊  那種…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不許抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起你就是這些傢伙的領班了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:18:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  連同主舞台都交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.98,0:19:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬喬喬…喬先生  恭喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可兒江大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我把事情鬧大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉媞琺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你立大功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好看看四周
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷你舞台的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的職員
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海盜船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些全都免費到手了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑得根本停不下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結局皆大歡喜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人需要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五十鈴小姐  請你手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堤拉米  你有什麼遺言嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直相信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同伴不會對我做這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個笑話真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我們不是你的同伴  所以下手也OK吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呵  這可真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你竟然是代理經理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.82,0:21:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有何貴幹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  我只是來看看情況
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說最近這裡的運營有所好轉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒做什麼大不了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原大明星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.57,0:22:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  最終檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.82,0:22:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.50,0:22:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  完美
